Package: geospatialsuite
Title: Comprehensive Geospatial Analysis and Modeling Toolkit for
    Multimodal Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Olatunde", "Akanbi", , "oda10@case.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for geospatial analysis including
    vegetation indices (NDVI, EVI, SAVI and 20+ others), water quality
    analysis, both NDWI variants, raster mosaicking, universal spatial
    joins, CDL crop analysis with comprehensive crop codes, spatial
    interpolation, temporal analysis, terrain analysis, and dynamic
    visualization. Designed for agricultural research, environmental
    monitoring, water quality assessment, and land use analysis with
    support for any geographic region and robust error handling.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
